      <hedline>
        <hl1>A Jail Under Scrutiny</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Anne Kaplan letter on August 24 article on Webcams set up in Maricopa County (Ariz) jail notes parents of Scott Norberg, who died while in custody, have sued and won $8 million settlement and jail has been criticized by Amnesty International</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I noticed some omissions in ''Hoping People Watch Jail and Won't Want to Visit'' (Aug. 24), about the Webcams set up in the Maricopa County jail in Arizona. The parents of Scott Norberg, who died while in custody, have not only sued the jail, but have won an $8 million settlement. Also, the Maricopa County jail has been criticized by Amnesty International.</p>
        <p>ANNE KAPLAN  Phoenix</p>
      </block>
